  <acronym>FABULOUS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicenter Longitudinal Observational Study to Assess the Effectiveness of Fimasartan-based Antihypertensive Treatment and Prognosis in Post-Acute Phase of Ischemic Stroke or Transient Ischemic Attack</official_title>
