  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effectiveness of fimasartan-based antihypertensive treatment and
      prognosis in post-acute phase of ischemic stroke or transient ischemic attack patients. All
      participants will receive fimasartan, and the investigators will follow them up for 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
